{"id":4438,"date":"2023-02-24T13:00:57","date_gmt":"2023-02-24T18:00:57","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/animalsevent.test\/?p=4438"},"modified":"2023-04-28T13:46:10","modified_gmt":"2023-04-28T17:46:10","slug":"what-happens-with-cats-when-their-owners-die","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/animalsevent.test\/what-happens-with-cats-when-their-owners-die\/","title":{"rendered":"3 Easy Steps When Owners Die: Planning for Your Pet&#8217;s Future"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What Happens With Cats When Their Owners Die<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As a lifelong animal lover and expert, I've seen countless heartbreaking situations where pets are left without their owners due to unfortunate circumstances such as death. In this article, we'll be focusing on cats and what happens to them when their owners pass away. We'll also be discussing what you can do to ensure your feline friend is taken care of in case something happens to you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><style>.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn{margin-top:1em;}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .kt-btn-wrap:nth-child(2), .kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .wp-block-kadence-singlebtn:nth-of-type(2){display:none;}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-column{max-height:174px;overflow-y:hidden;-webkit-mask-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, black 50%, transparent 100%);mask-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, black 50%, transparent 100%);}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46.kb-smc-open > .wp-block-kadence-column{max-height:none;-webkit-mask-image:none;mask-image:none;}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46.kb-smc-open > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .kt-btn-wrap:nth-child(1), .kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46.kb-smc-open > .wp-block-k